thread.title: Terry Williams

author: Terry Williams
title: Terry Williams
text: The folks at Candy Warehouse are AWESOME!!! Super-friendly and super-helpful in getting my rush order out IMMEDIATELY so I could receive it on time! Calling in proved to be quicker than the online chat, but that could be chalked up to just being busy. And even then, the person manning the chat line was interested in following up, just to make sure everything went okay for me. I really appreciate everyone's help - THANK YOU!!!
